title: tour: [short description of the issue]
body:
Context: /flowcontrol/7

The output doesn't seem to change if I change the order of the items in the fmt.Println statement.

The output for 
fmt.Println(
		pow(3, 2, 10),
		pow(3, 3, 20),
	)

is

27 >= 20
9 20

Why isn't the output

9 20
27 >= 20

?
